OL,3,CMan, 28, admits arson after fire guts
OL,4,CLabour MP's office
OL,6,FA 28-year-old man has admitted to
OL,7,Farson after a major fire at an MP's
OL,8,Fconstituency office.
OL,10,FJoshua Oliver, of no fixed address,
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to starting the fire
OL,12,Fwhich destroyed the premises of Sharon
OL,13,FHodgson, Labour MP for Washington and
OL,14,FGateshead South, which happened in the
OL,15,Fearly hours of Thursday.
OL,17,FThe guilty plea was entered at
OL,18,FNewcastle Magistrates' Court on the
OL,19,Fbasis that it was reckless rather than
OL,20,Fintentional.
