OL,6,FThe Crown did not accept that basis of
OL,7,Fthe plea.
OL,9,FThe fire gutted the premises, as well
OL,10,Fas those of a small charity for people
OL,11,Fwith very rare genetic diseases and an
OL,12,FNHS mental health service for
OL,13,Fveterans, which were based in the same
OL,14,Fbuilding.
OL,16,FOliver had been living in a tent
OL,17,Fnearby, the court heard.
OL,19,FDistrict Judge Kate Meek remanded him
OL,20,Fin custody to appear at Newcastle
OL,21,FCrown Court on October 14.
